review.reviewBody: I love Earls. I love the South Indian Chicken Curry, I love the dynamite rolls.  I love the chicken wings. I love the service. Just go here; you won't regret it. Or order on DoorDash. They pack their takeout well.

Props to the Kitchen staff working late on sept 19th! Food was exceptionally good. Pulled Chicken Clubhouse was the best I've had to date.  Pumpkin Pie was flavourful and served with a generous portion of whipped cream. Very pleased.
BBQ Back Ribs (Full) were tender and delicious.  Definitely one of my favourite picks.
Bring back the pecan bourbon pie. This Strawberry Cream Pie needs to go.
